    message: Two prompt-stale details are inconsistently formatted — one is target-prefixed, one is not.
    reasoning: '"{target}: not generated" carries the target prefix; "prompt changed since gen" does not, even though it is also produced per declared target inside the same loop. Unclear whether the missing prefix is deliberate or an oversight. Taken literally (and as implemented), the bare string is emitted.'
